mlcpp
=====
INSTALL
=====
1. Create "external" symbol link pointing to your local include (usually /usr/local/include).
2. Create "lib" symbol link pointing to your local lib (usually /usr/local/lib).
3. Install gflags and glog.
4. Make.

====
decision trees
====
1. Data files are space-separated with label in the first column.
2. You need a feature file (--feature_file) to specify name of each feature in data files.
3. See tree/gen_bagging_train_cmd and tree/gen_bagging_eval_cmd for example command for training and evaluation.
